The paper presents a parallel approximation algorithm for a class of semidefinite programs, which involves optimization and numerical analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) which covers optimization and approximation algorithms. The paper also involves parallel computing, which suggests the category cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The numerical analysis aspect of the paper suggests the category cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). The paper also involves machine learning, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves information theory, which suggests the category cs.IT (Information Theory).
